{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01T4WKVm7wdB4nLSnnbkfAez","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me provide the comprehensive exploration report:\n\n## Referral Feature Frontend - Complete E2E Flow Analysis\n\nI've explored the entire referral system frontend code. Here's the comprehensive user flow breakdown for E2E testing:\n\n### File Structure Overview\n\n**Core Referral Components** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/`):\n- `ReferralPage.tsx` — Main landing page (requires wallet + auth)\n- `ReferralLinkCard.tsx` — Create/display referral code\n- `ReferralStatsCard.tsx` — Stats summary (4 cards: referred count, active 7d, volume, earned)\n- `ReferralClaimCard.tsx` — Pending earnings display + claim button + poll mechanism\n- `ReferralEarningsTable.tsx` — Paginated earnings history (20 per page)\n- `hooks/useReferralApply.ts` — Auto-apply referral code from localStorage after auth\n- `index.ts` — Exports `useReferralApply` and `ReferralPage`\n\n**API Layer** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/lib/referral-api.ts`):\n- Fetch wrappers for 8 backend endpoints\n- All endpoints use JWT Bearer auth\n\n**Profile Integration** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileSettings.tsx`):\n- Shows referrer status (if linked)\n- Manual referral code input form (only if not yet linked)\n- Error handling for self-referral, already linked, code not found\n\n**Router Setup** (`App.tsx` at `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/`):\n- Route `/referrals` → `ReferralPage` (with `RouteErrorBoundary`)\n- Route `/r/:code` → `ReferralCapture` component (stores code in localStorage, redirects to `/`)\n- `useReferralApply()` hook called in `AppContent()` to auto-apply stored codes\n\n---\n\n### Complete E2E User Flows\n\n#### **Flow 1: Join Via Referral Link**\n**Entry**: User clicks `taunt.bet/r/{code}` (from social, Discord, etc.)\n\n1. **URL capture** (`ReferralCapture` component):\n   - Route `/r/:code` is hit\n   - Component extracts `{code}` from URL params\n   - Stores in localStorage: `{ \"referral_code\": { code: \"...\", capturedAt: \"ISO timestamp\" } }`\n   - Redirects to `/` (navigate, no error boundary)\n\n2. **Wallet connection** (standard flow):\n   - User sees \"Connect wallet\" prompt in header\n   - Clicks wallet button → signs message → authenticated\n\n3. **Auto-apply on auth** (`useReferralApply` hook):\n   - After `isAuthenticated`, `accessToken`, and `address` are all present:\n   - Reads localStorage for `referral_code` key\n   - Extracts stored code\n   - Calls `POST /referral/apply` with code\n   - **Success path**: Clears localStorage, logs console warning\n   - **Permanent error path** (self-referral, already linked, code invalid): Clears localStorage, stops\n   - **Transient error path** (network/500): Keeps localStorage, retries on next auth\n   - Prevents duplicate calls via `appliedRef.current` guard\n\n4. **User sees confirmation**:\n   - No inline toast yet (TODO in code)\n   - User navigates to `/profile` → Settings tab\n   - Shows \"Referred by: [truncated wallet]\" with link icon\n\n**Test checkpoints**:\n- Code stored in localStorage after /r/:code visit\n- Auto-apply makes POST /referral/apply with correct code\n- referrer status displayed in ProfileSettings\n- Duplicate apply prevention works (refresh doesn't re-apply)\n\n---\n\n#### **Flow 2: Claim Referral Code (Own Referral Page)**\n**Entry**: Authenticated user navigates to `/referrals` page\n\n1. **Page load** (`ReferralPage`):\n   - Checks `connected` (wallet) and `isAuthenticated` (JWT)\n   - If either false: shows unauthenticated prompt\n   - If true: renders 4 child components in parallel\n\n2. **ReferralLinkCard component** (create or edit code):\n   - **On mount**: `getReferralCode()` fetch (GET `/referral/code`)\n   - **Loading state**: Shows skeleton\n   - **No code**: Form to set new code\n     - Input validation: 3-16 chars, lowercase letters/numbers/hyphens only\n     - Submit button disabled if error or empty\n     - On submit: `setReferralCode()` (POST `/referral/code`) → displays URL\n   - **Code exists**: Display mode\n     - Shows read-only input with full URL: `taunt.bet/r/{code}`\n     - Copy button copies URL to clipboard → \"Copied!\" feedback for 2s\n     - Change link allows editing (shows form again)\n   - **Error handling**: Displays inline error messages\n\n   **Test checkpoints**:\n   - Validation works (too short, too long, invalid chars)\n   - Copy button copies correct URL\n   - Change button toggles edit mode\n   - POST /referral/code updates display\n\n3. **ReferralStatsCard component** (summary stats):\n   - **On mount**: `getReferralStats()` (GET `/referral/stats`)\n   - **Loading**: Shows 4 skeleton boxes\n   - **Loaded**: Displays 4 stat boxes with formatting:\n     - Referred Players: plain number\n     - Active (7d): plain number\n     - Total Volume: formatted SOL (M/k/base with precision)\n     - Total Earned: formatted SOL\n   - No error UI; shows zeros on fetch failure\n\n   **Test checkpoints**:\n   - Stats fetch succeeds and displays formatted values\n   - SOL formatting works correctly (0.0001, 0.012, 1.23, 1.5k, 2.3M)\n\n4. **ReferralClaimCard component** (pending earnings + claim flow):\n   - **On mount**: `getReferralStats()` → sets `stats` state\n   - **Display pending earnings**:\n     - Large balance display: formatted pending lamports\n     - Breakdown table: \"From referrals\" + \"From fee rebates\" (each formatted SOL)\n   - **Claim flow**:\n     - Button state depends on `pendingLamports >= 10_000_000` (0.01 SOL min):\n       - If insufficient: \"Below minimum (0.01 SOL)\" (disabled)\n       - If zero: \"No pending earnings\" (disabled)\n       - If ready: \"Claim Earnings\" (enabled)\n       - If claiming: \"Claiming...\" (disabled)\n       - If pending status: \"Processing...\" (disabled)\n     - Click → `requestReferralClaim()` (POST `/referral/claim`)\n     - Returns `{ claimId, amountLamports, status: \"pending\", txSignature? }`\n     - **Poll loop starts**:\n       - Every 2-3s, calls `pollClaimStatus()` (GET `/referral/claim/{claimId}`)\n       - Updates local state with new status\n       - On `status === \"completed\"`: refreshes stats + shows success\n         - Shows \"Claimed {amount} SOL\" with explorer link (opens in new tab)\n         - TX signature comes from poll response\n       - On `status === \"failed\"`: shows error message, stops poll\n       - On other errors: keeps polling (5s backoff)\n   - **Error UI**:\n     - Shows error from POST /referral/claim or network failures\n\n   **Test checkpoints**:\n   - Min claim threshold enforced (0.01 SOL)\n   - Claim button disabled when below minimum\n   - POST /referral/claim returns claim ID\n   - Poll starts immediately (2s delay first)\n   - Poll updates status correctly\n   - Success message shows with TX link\n   - Stats refresh after successful claim\n   - Cleanup: poll interval cleared on unmount\n\n5. **ReferralEarningsTable component** (paginated history):\n   - **On mount**: `getReferralEarnings()` (GET `/referral/earnings?page=1&limit=20`)\n   - **Loading**: Shows 3 skeleton rows\n   - **No earnings**: \"No earnings yet. Share your link to start earning!\"\n   - **Earnings present**: Table with columns:\n     - Date: MM/DD HH:MM format\n     - Game: \"Coinflip\", \"Lord of RNGs\", etc.\n     - Referee: Truncated wallet (first 4 + last 4 chars)\n     - Wager: Formatted SOL\n     - Your Earning: \"+Formatted SOL\" (green highlight)\n   - **Pagination**:\n     - Shows \"page / totalPages\"\n     - Prev/Next buttons (disabled at boundaries)\n     - Fetches new page on click\n\n   **Test checkpoints**:\n   - Table renders with correct columns\n   - Date format correct\n   - Wallet truncation works\n   - SOL formatting consistent\n   - Pagination navigation works\n   - Page state persists in component local state\n\n---\n\n#### **Flow 3: Apply Code from Profile Settings**\n**Entry**: Authenticated user navigates to `/profile` → Settings tab\n\n1. **ProfileSettings component load**:\n   - **On mount**: `getReferrer()` (GET `/referral/referrer`)\n   - **Already linked**: Shows \"Referred by: [wallet]\" with link icon (green)\n     - No code input shown\n     - No ability to change referrer (one-way)\n   - **Not linked**: Shows form\n     - Input field: \"Enter referral code\"\n     - Apply button\n     - Error message space below form\n\n2. **User submits code**:\n   - Input is lowercase-trimmed\n   - Empty check: shows error \"Please enter a referral code\"\n   - Click Apply → `applyReferralCode()` (POST `/referral/apply`)\n   - Button shows \"Applying...\" (disabled)\n\n3. **Response handling**:\n   - **Success** (referrer returned):\n     - Sets referrer wallet in state\n     - Shows success message: \"Referral code applied! You now receive a 10% fee rebate on all games.\"\n     - Clears input\n     - Form replaced with \"Referred by: [wallet]\"\n   - **Self-referral error** (SELF_REFERRAL in message):\n     - Shows \"You cannot use your own referral code\"\n   - **Already linked error** (ALREADY_LINKED in message):\n     - Shows \"You are already linked to a referrer\"\n   - **Code not found error** (NOT_FOUND in message):\n     - Shows \"Referral code not found\"\n   - **Other errors**:\n     - Shows raw error message from API\n\n4. **UX details**:\n   - Input disabled while applying\n   - Apply button disabled if input empty or applying\n   - On keydown Enter: auto-submit if not applying\n   - Setting error clears error on new input keystroke\n\n**Test checkpoints**:\n- getReferrer() fetch on mount\n- Already-linked state prevents form display\n- Error detection logic (self-referral, already linked, not found)\n- Success state shows confirmation + hides form\n- Form state clears on success\n- Error messages are user-friendly (not raw API codes)\n\n---\n\n### API Contracts (Backend Dependencies)\n\n**Endpoints all use Bearer JWT auth in Authorization header**:\n\n| Endpoint | Method | Request | Response | Notes |\n|----------|--------|---------|----------|-------|\n| `/referral/code` | POST | `{ code: string }` | `{ code, url }` | Set/replace code |\n| `/referral/code` | GET | — | `{ code, url }` | Get current code (404 if none) |\n| `/referral/apply` | POST | `{ code: string }` | `{ referrer: string, benefit: string }` | Link to referrer |\n| `/referral/referrer` | GET | — | `{ referrerWallet, linkedAt }` | Get referrer (404 if none) |\n| `/referral/stats` | GET | — | `{ referredCount, activeCount, totalVolumeLamports, totalEarnedLamports, totalRebateLamports, pendingLamports }` | Summary stats |\n| `/referral/earnings` | GET | `?page=1&limit=20` | `{ items: [...], pagination: { page, totalPages } }` | Per-game earning history |\n| `/referral/claim` | POST | — | `{ claimId, amountLamports, status: \"pending\", txSignature? }` | Request earnings payout |\n| `/referral/claim/{claimId}` | GET | — | `{ claimId, amountLamports, status, txSignature? }` | Poll claim status |\n\n**Error handling**:\n- 404 responses thrown as errors (handled gracefully for code/referrer endpoints)\n- Error response: `{ error: string \\| { message: string } }`\n- Frontend parses and displays user-friendly messages\n\n---\n\n### Key E2E Testing Requirements\n\n1. **Referral Link Capture**:\n   - Navigate to `/r/test-code`\n   - Verify localStorage contains referral code\n   - Verify redirect to `/` happens\n   - Verify auto-apply on next auth (mock API or real backend)\n\n2. **Referral Code Management**:\n   - Create code via ReferralLinkCard form\n   - Verify POST succeeds and URL displays\n   - Copy URL and verify clipboard\n   - Change code and verify update\n   - Validation errors show correctly\n\n3. **Earnings & Claims**:\n   - Load ReferralClaimCard with pending earnings\n   - Verify claim button disabled below 0.01 SOL\n   - Click claim → POST /referral/claim\n   - Verify polling starts (GET /referral/claim/{id})\n   - Verify status transitions (pending → completed)\n   - Verify TX link appears and is clickable\n   - Verify stats refresh after claim\n\n4. **Earnings Table Pagination**:\n   - Load table with earnings\n   - Verify columns render (date, game, referee, wager, earning)\n   - Verify pagination buttons work\n   - Verify page info updates\n\n5. **Profile Settings Integration**:\n   - Navigate to /profile → Settings\n   - If already linked: verify referrer displays\n   - If not linked: verify form shows\n   - Apply valid code → verify success message\n   - Apply self-referral → verify error\n   - Apply unknown code → verify \"not found\" error\n   - Apply when already linked → verify \"already linked\" error\n\n6. **Auto-Apply Flow**:\n   - Visit /r/{code} without wallet\n   - Connect wallet (triggers auth)\n   - Verify useReferralApply hook auto-submits code\n   - Verify localStorage cleared on success\n   - Verify no duplicate submissions on page refresh\n\n---\n\n### E2E Test Infrastructure\n\nThe codebase uses **Playwright** with custom fixtures (see `e2e/local/fixtures`). Test patterns:\n- `test.describe()` for grouping\n- Dual-player fixtures (`playerAPage`, `playerBPage`) for multi-user scenarios\n- Page object helpers in `e2e/local/helpers/page-objects.ts`\n- Console error tracking via `po.trackConsoleErrors()`\n- Fixtures from `./fixtures` (custom setup)\n\nExample pattern from `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/00-smoke.spec.ts`:\n```typescript\ntest(\"app loads\", async ({ playerAPage }) => {\n  await playerAPage.goto(\"/\", { waitUntil: \"networkidle\" });\n  await expect(playerAPage.locator(\".header\")).toBeVisible({ timeout: 10_000 });\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n### Critical Implementation Details\n\n- **localStorage key**: `\"referral_code\"` → `{ code, capturedAt }`\n- **Apply duplicate prevention**: `appliedRef.current` flag\n- **Min claim amount**: 10,000,000 lamports (0.01 SOL)\n- **Poll timing**: 2s initial delay, 3s normal, 5s on error\n- **Code validation**: `/^[a-z0-9-]{3,16}$/`\n- **Wallet truncation**: First 4 + last 4 characters\n- **Date format**: MM/DD HH:MM (24-hour, ISO parsed then formatted)\n- **SOL format precision**: 4-2 decimals depending on magnitude\n- **Error keywords for detection**: SELF_REFERRAL, ALREADY_LINKED, NOT_FOUND, INVALID\n\n---\n\n### File Paths (Absolute)\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralPage.tsx`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralLinkCard.tsx`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralStatsCard.tsx`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralClaimCard.tsx`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralEarningsTable.tsx`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/hooks/useReferralApply.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/index.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/lib/referral-api.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileSettings.tsx`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx` (routes + ReferralCapture)"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a303c7509ce3cada2 (use SendMessage with to: 'a303c7509ce3cada2' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 52305\ntool_uses: 20\nduration_ms: 93100</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"18302c5c-b9ec-4f75-9de3-1cbb537277bf","uuid":"259478bc-8caa-41ae-8ac5-ac4a81fa702b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T14:09:41.767Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the referral feature frontend code in /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/. Read all files:\n1. ReferralPage.tsx\n2. ReferralLinkCard.tsx\n3. ReferralStatsCard.tsx\n4. ReferralClaimCard.tsx\n5. ReferralEarningsTable.tsx\n6. hooks/useReferralApply.ts\n7. index.ts\n\nAlso check the /r/:code route in App.tsx and the referral section in ProfileSettings.tsx. I need to understand the full user flow for E2E testing.","agentId":"a303c7509ce3cada2","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me provide the comprehensive exploration report:\n\n## Referral Feature Frontend - Complete E2E Flow Analysis\n\nI've explored the entire referral system frontend code. Here's the comprehensive user flow breakdown for E2E testing:\n\n### File Structure Overview\n\n**Core Referral Components** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/`):\n- `ReferralPage.tsx` — Main landing page (requires wallet + auth)\n- `ReferralLinkCard.tsx` — Create/display referral code\n- `ReferralStatsCard.tsx` — Stats summary (4 cards: referred count, active 7d, volume, earned)\n- `ReferralClaimCard.tsx` — Pending earnings display + claim button + poll mechanism\n- `ReferralEarningsTable.tsx` — Paginated earnings history (20 per page)\n- `hooks/useReferralApply.ts` — Auto-apply referral code from localStorage after auth\n- `index.ts` — Exports `useReferralApply` and `ReferralPage`\n\n**API Layer** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/lib/referral-api.ts`):\n- Fetch wrappers for 8 backend endpoints\n- All endpoints use JWT Bearer auth\n\n**Profile Integration** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileSettings.tsx`):\n- Shows referrer status (if linked)\n- Manual referral code input form (only if not yet linked)\n- Error handling for self-referral, already linked, code not found\n\n**Router Setup** (`App.tsx` at `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/`):\n- Route `/referrals` → `ReferralPage` (with `RouteErrorBoundary`)\n- Route `/r/:code` → `ReferralCapture` component (stores code in localStorage, redirects to `/`)\n- `useReferralApply()` hook called in `AppContent()` to auto-apply stored codes\n\n---\n\n### Complete E2E User Flows\n\n#### **Flow 1: Join Via Referral Link**\n**Entry**: User clicks `taunt.bet/r/{code}` (from social, Discord, etc.)\n\n1. **URL capture** (`ReferralCapture` component):\n   - Route `/r/:code` is hit\n   - Component extracts `{code}` from URL params\n   - Stores in localStorage: `{ \"referral_code\": { code: \"...\", capturedAt: \"ISO timestamp\" } }`\n   - Redirects to `/` (navigate, no error boundary)\n\n2. **Wallet connection** (standard flow):\n   - User sees \"Connect wallet\" prompt in header\n   - Clicks wallet button → signs message → authenticated\n\n3. **Auto-apply on auth** (`useReferralApply` hook):\n   - After `isAuthenticated`, `accessToken`, and `address` are all present:\n   - Reads localStorage for `referral_code` key\n   - Extracts stored code\n   - Calls `POST /referral/apply` with code\n   - **Success path**: Clears localStorage, logs console warning\n   - **Permanent error path** (self-referral, already linked, code invalid): Clears localStorage, stops\n   - **Transient error path** (network/500): Keeps localStorage, retries on next auth\n   - Prevents duplicate calls via `appliedRef.current` guard\n\n4. **User sees confirmation**:\n   - No inline toast yet (TODO in code)\n   - User navigates to `/profile` → Settings tab\n   - Shows \"Referred by: [truncated wallet]\" with link icon\n\n**Test checkpoints**:\n- Code stored in localStorage after /r/:code visit\n- Auto-apply makes POST /referral/apply with correct code\n- referrer status displayed in ProfileSettings\n- Duplicate apply prevention works (refresh doesn't re-apply)\n\n---\n\n#### **Flow 2: Claim Referral Code (Own Referral Page)**\n**Entry**: Authenticated user navigates to `/referrals` page\n\n1. **Page load** (`ReferralPage`):\n   - Checks `connected` (wallet) and `isAuthenticated` (JWT)\n   - If either false: shows unauthenticated prompt\n   - If true: renders 4 child components in parallel\n\n2. **ReferralLinkCard component** (create or edit code):\n   - **On mount**: `getReferralCode()` fetch (GET `/referral/code`)\n   - **Loading state**: Shows skeleton\n   - **No code**: Form to set new code\n     - Input validation: 3-16 chars, lowercase letters/numbers/hyphens only\n     - Submit button disabled if error or empty\n     - On submit: `setReferralCode()` (POST `/referral/code`) → displays URL\n   - **Code exists**: Display mode\n     - Shows read-only input with full URL: `taunt.bet/r/{code}`\n     - Copy button copies URL to clipboard → \"Copied!\" feedback for 2s\n     - Change link allows editing (shows form again)\n   - **Error handling**: Displays inline error messages\n\n   **Test checkpoints**:\n   - Validation works (too short, too long, invalid chars)\n   - Copy button copies correct URL\n   - Change button toggles edit mode\n   - POST /referral/code updates display\n\n3. **ReferralStatsCard component** (summary stats):\n   - **On mount**: `getReferralStats()` (GET `/referral/stats`)\n   - **Loading**: Shows 4 skeleton boxes\n   - **Loaded**: Displays 4 stat boxes with formatting:\n     - Referred Players: plain number\n     - Active (7d): plain number\n     - Total Volume: formatted SOL (M/k/base with precision)\n     - Total Earned: formatted SOL\n   - No error UI; shows zeros on fetch failure\n\n   **Test checkpoints**:\n   - Stats fetch succeeds and displays formatted values\n   - SOL formatting works correctly (0.0001, 0.012, 1.23, 1.5k, 2.3M)\n\n4. **ReferralClaimCard component** (pending earnings + claim flow):\n   - **On mount**: `getReferralStats()` → sets `stats` state\n   - **Display pending earnings**:\n     - Large balance display: formatted pending lamports\n     - Breakdown table: \"From referrals\" + \"From fee rebates\" (each formatted SOL)\n   - **Claim flow**:\n     - Button state depends on `pendingLamports >= 10_000_000` (0.01 SOL min):\n       - If insufficient: \"Below minimum (0.01 SOL)\" (disabled)\n       - If zero: \"No pending earnings\" (disabled)\n       - If ready: \"Claim Earnings\" (enabled)\n       - If claiming: \"Claiming...\" (disabled)\n       - If pending status: \"Processing...\" (disabled)\n     - Click → `requestReferralClaim()` (POST `/referral/claim`)\n     - Returns `{ claimId, amountLamports, status: \"pending\", txSignature? }`\n     - **Poll loop starts**:\n       - Every 2-3s, calls `pollClaimStatus()` (GET `/referral/claim/{claimId}`)\n       - Updates local state with new status\n       - On `status === \"completed\"`: refreshes stats + shows success\n         - Shows \"Claimed {amount} SOL\" with explorer link (opens in new tab)\n         - TX signature comes from poll response\n       - On `status === \"failed\"`: shows error message, stops poll\n       - On other errors: keeps polling (5s backoff)\n   - **Error UI**:\n     - Shows error from POST /referral/claim or network failures\n\n   **Test checkpoints**:\n   - Min claim threshold enforced (0.01 SOL)\n   - Claim button disabled when below minimum\n   - POST /referral/claim returns claim ID\n   - Poll starts immediately (2s delay first)\n   - Poll updates status correctly\n   - Success message shows with TX link\n   - Stats refresh after successful claim\n   - Cleanup: poll interval cleared on unmount\n\n5. **ReferralEarningsTable component** (paginated history):\n   - **On mount**: `getReferralEarnings()` (GET `/referral/earnings?page=1&limit=20`)\n   - **Loading**: Shows 3 skeleton rows\n   - **No earnings**: \"No earnings yet. Share your link to start earning!\"\n   - **Earnings present**: Table with columns:\n     - Date: MM/DD HH:MM format\n     - Game: \"Coinflip\", \"Lord of RNGs\", etc.\n     - Referee: Truncated wallet (first 4 + last 4 chars)\n     - Wager: Formatted SOL\n     - Your Earning: \"+Formatted SOL\" (green highlight)\n   - **Pagination**:\n     - Shows \"page / totalPages\"\n     - Prev/Next buttons (disabled at boundaries)\n     - Fetches new page on click\n\n   **Test checkpoints**:\n   - Table renders with correct columns\n   - Date format correct\n   - Wallet truncation works\n   - SOL formatting consistent\n   - Pagination navigation works\n   - Page state persists in component local state\n\n---\n\n#### **Flow 3: Apply Code from Profile Settings**\n**Entry**: Authenticated user navigates to `/profile` → Settings tab\n\n1. **ProfileSettings component load**:\n   - **On mount**: `getReferrer()` (GET `/referral/referrer`)\n   - **Already linked**: Shows \"Referred by: [wallet]\" with link icon (green)\n     - No code input shown\n     - No ability to change referrer (one-way)\n   - **Not linked**: Shows form\n     - Input field: \"Enter referral code\"\n     - Apply button\n     - Error message space below form\n\n2. **User submits code**:\n   - Input is lowercase-trimmed\n   - Empty check: shows error \"Please enter a referral code\"\n   - Click Apply → `applyReferralCode()` (POST `/referral/apply`)\n   - Button shows \"Applying...\" (disabled)\n\n3. **Response handling**:\n   - **Success** (referrer returned):\n     - Sets referrer wallet in state\n     - Shows success message: \"Referral code applied! You now receive a 10% fee rebate on all games.\"\n     - Clears input\n     - Form replaced with \"Referred by: [wallet]\"\n   - **Self-referral error** (SELF_REFERRAL in message):\n     - Shows \"You cannot use your own referral code\"\n   - **Already linked error** (ALREADY_LINKED in message):\n     - Shows \"You are already linked to a referrer\"\n   - **Code not found error** (NOT_FOUND in message):\n     - Shows \"Referral code not found\"\n   - **Other errors**:\n     - Shows raw error message from API\n\n4. **UX details**:\n   - Input disabled while applying\n   - Apply button disabled if input empty or applying\n   - On keydown Enter: auto-submit if not applying\n   - Setting error clears error on new input keystroke\n\n**Test checkpoints**:\n- getReferrer() fetch on mount\n- Already-linked state prevents form display\n- Error detection logic (self-referral, already linked, not found)\n- Success state shows confirmation + hides form\n- Form state clears on success\n- Error messages are user-friendly (not raw API codes)\n\n---\n\n### API Contracts (Backend Dependencies)\n\n**Endpoints all use Bearer JWT auth in Authorization header**:\n\n| Endpoint | Method | Request | Response | Notes |\n|----------|--------|---------|----------|-------|\n| `/referral/code` | POST | `{ code: string }` | `{ code, url }` | Set/replace code |\n| `/referral/code` | GET | — | `{ code, url }` | Get current code (404 if none) |\n| `/referral/apply` | POST | `{ code: string }` | `{ referrer: string, benefit: string }` | Link to referrer |\n| `/referral/referrer` | GET | — | `{ referrerWallet, linkedAt }` | Get referrer (404 if none) |\n| `/referral/stats` | GET | — | `{ referredCount, activeCount, totalVolumeLamports, totalEarnedLamports, totalRebateLamports, pendingLamports }` | Summary stats |\n| `/referral/earnings` | GET | `?page=1&limit=20` | `{ items: [...], pagination: { page, totalPages } }` | Per-game earning history |\n| `/referral/claim` | POST | — | `{ claimId, amountLamports, status: \"pending\", txSignature? }` | Request earnings payout |\n| `/referral/claim/{claimId}` | GET | — | `{ claimId, amountLamports, status, txSignature? }` | Poll claim status |\n\n**Error handling**:\n- 404 responses thrown as errors (handled gracefully for code/referrer endpoints)\n- Error response: `{ error: string \\| { message: string } }`\n- Frontend parses and displays user-friendly messages\n\n---\n\n### Key E2E Testing Requirements\n\n1. **Referral Link Capture**:\n   - Navigate to `/r/test-code`\n   - Verify localStorage contains referral code\n   - Verify redirect to `/` happens\n   - Verify auto-apply on next auth (mock API or real backend)\n\n2. **Referral Code Management**:\n   - Create code via ReferralLinkCard form\n   - Verify POST succeeds and URL displays\n   - Copy URL and verify clipboard\n   - Change code and verify update\n   - Validation errors show correctly\n\n3. **Earnings & Claims**:\n   - Load ReferralClaimCard with pending earnings\n   - Verify claim button disabled below 0.01 SOL\n   - Click claim → POST /referral/claim\n   - Verify polling starts (GET /referral/claim/{id})\n   - Verify status transitions (pending → completed)\n   - Verify TX link appears and is clickable\n   - Verify stats refresh after claim\n\n4. **Earnings Table Pagination**:\n   - Load table with earnings\n   - Verify columns render (date, game, referee, wager, earning)\n   - Verify pagination buttons work\n   - Verify page info updates\n\n5. **Profile Settings Integration**:\n   - Navigate to /profile → Settings\n   - If already linked: verify referrer displays\n   - If not linked: verify form shows\n   - Apply valid code → verify success message\n   - Apply self-referral → verify error\n   - Apply unknown code → verify \"not found\" error\n   - Apply when already linked → verify \"already linked\" error\n\n6. **Auto-Apply Flow**:\n   - Visit /r/{code} without wallet\n   - Connect wallet (triggers auth)\n   - Verify useReferralApply hook auto-submits code\n   - Verify localStorage cleared on success\n   - Verify no duplicate submissions on page refresh\n\n---\n\n### E2E Test Infrastructure\n\nThe codebase uses **Playwright** with custom fixtures (see `e2e/local/fixtures`). Test patterns:\n- `test.describe()` for grouping\n- Dual-player fixtures (`playerAPage`, `playerBPage`) for multi-user scenarios\n- Page object helpers in `e2e/local/helpers/page-objects.ts`\n- Console error tracking via `po.trackConsoleErrors()`\n- Fixtures from `./fixtures` (custom setup)\n\nExample pattern from `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/00-smoke.spec.ts`:\n```typescript\ntest(\"app loads\", async ({ playerAPage }) => {\n  await playerAPage.goto(\"/\", { waitUntil: \"networkidle\" });\n  await expect(playerAPage.locator(\".header\")).toBeVisible({ timeout: 10_000 });\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n### Critical Implementation Details\n\n- **localStorage key**: `\"referral_code\"` → `{ code, capturedAt }`\n- **Apply duplicate prevention**: `appliedRef.current` flag\n- **Min claim amount**: 10,000,000 lamports (0.01 SOL)\n- **Poll timing**: 2s initial delay, 3s normal, 5s on error\n- **Code validation**: `/^[a-z0-9-]{3,16}$/`\n- **Wallet truncation**: First 4 + last 4 characters\n- **Date format**: MM/DD HH:MM (24-hour, ISO parsed then formatted)\n- **SOL format precision**: 4-2 decimals depending on magnitude\n- **Error keywords for detection**: SELF_REFERRAL, ALREADY_LINKED, NOT_FOUND, INVALID\n\n---\n\n### File Paths (Absolute)\n\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralPage.tsx`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralLinkCard.tsx`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralStatsCard.tsx`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralClaimCard.tsx`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/ReferralEarningsTable.tsx`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/hooks/useReferralApply.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/index.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/lib/referral-api.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfileSettings.tsx`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx` (routes + ReferralCapture)"}],"totalDurationMs":93100,"totalTokens":52305,"totalToolUseCount":2