ps'.\n@rng-utopia/backend:typecheck:   Property 'sql' is missing in type '{ db: Db; connection: Connection; serverKey: PublicKey; isWorkerRunning: () => true; minSolBalance: number; }' but required in type 'HealthDeps'.\n@rng-utopia/backend:typecheck:  ELIFECYCLE  Command failed with exit code 2.\n@rng-utopia/backend:typecheck: ERROR: command finished with error: command (/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend) /home/vscode/.local/share/pnpm/.tools/pnpm/9.15.0/bin/pnpm run typecheck exited (2)\n@rng-utopia/backend#typecheck: command (/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/services/backend) /home/vscode/.local/share/pnpm/.tools/pnpm/9.15.0/bin/pnpm run typecheck exited (2)\n\n Tasks:    16 successful, 18 total\nCached:    16 cached, 18 total\n  Time:    24.12s \nFailed:    @rng-utopia/backend#typecheck\n\n ERROR  run failed: command  exited (2)\n ELIFECYCLE  Command failed with exit code 2.","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
